mixin features_screen 
    +b.features-wrap.wrap
        +b.features.container 
            +b.title-default_center 
                +e.P.title.text_title-regular._blue Features
                +e.P.desc.text_big._gray._height-big Some of the features and advantages that we provide for those of you who store data in this Data Warehouse.
            +b.features-content
                +b.features-item_first
                    +e.IMG(src="./img/features-1.png").icon
                    +e.P.title.text_title-small._blue Search Data
                    +e.P.desc.text_regular-thin._gray._height-big Donâ€™t worry if your data is very large, the Data Warehoue provides a search engine, which is useful for making it easier to find data effectively saving time.
